      "text": "Worker\n   │\n   ▼\nRead device token from DB\n   │\n   ▼\nSend notification\n   │\n   ▼\nAPNs/FCM response\n   │\n   ├── Success\n   │      │\n   │      ▼\n   │   Keep token\n   │\n   └── Invalid token\n          │\n          ▼\n    Mark device inactive",
      "fontSize": 17.872946101517535,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Worker\n   │\n   ▼\nRead device token from DB\n   │\n   ▼\nSend notification\n   │\n   ▼\nAPNs/FCM response\n   │\n   ├── Success\n   │      │\n   │      ▼\n   │   Keep token\n   │\n   └── Invalid token\n          │\n          ▼\n    Mark device inactive",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
