      "text": "                Notification Request\n                        │\n                        ▼\n                  Message Queue\n                        │\n                        ▼\n                   Worker Process\n                        │\n            Create log entry (PENDING)\n                        │\n                        ▼\n                 Send to APNs/FCM\n                        │\n          ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐\n          │                           │\n       Success                     Failure\n          │                           │\n          ▼                           ▼\n Update log: SENT           Update log: FAILED",
      "fontSize": 20.006279434850864,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "                Notification Request\n                        │\n                        ▼\n                  Message Queue\n                        │\n                        ▼\n                   Worker Process\n                        │\n            Create log entry (PENDING)\n                        │\n                        ▼\n                 Send to APNs/FCM\n                        │\n          ┌─────────────┴─────────────┐\n          │                           │\n       Success                     Failure\n          │                           │\n          ▼                           ▼\n Update log: SENT           Update log: FAILED",
